<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Trust those Isengard bows</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">skitch</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Gandalf and Theoden lead their clans against your mighty army, while the Uruk Archers spill some blood...  Hope you got some bandaids...</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Frodo, Tired Traveller<br />
The One Ring, IB<br />
<br />
Adventure<br />
1.  (Get Legolas)<br />
2.  (Add 1 twilight when you assign somebody to a minion)<br />
3.  The Stables (exert Rohan man to play a Rohan steed from your draw deck)<br />
4.  (Exert Theoden or 2 companions)<br />
5.  The Deep of Helm (first Uruk -3 twilight)<br />
6.  The Hornbury <!--303-->Armory (play a possession to draw a card)<br />
7.  Exert every companion unless you have a Rohan companion<br />
8.  Wizard&#39;s Vale (i.e. the site every one not playing Dunland has to use...)<br />
9.  Palantir Chamber (remove 2 burdens to get a minion from d/c pile)<br />
<br />
Companions (13)<br />
<!--299-->Aragorn, Ranger of the North x 3<br />
Boromir, Defender of Minas Tirith<br />
Eomer, Third Marshall of the Riddermark (start)<br />
